1
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:14,560
<font color="yellow">- Maafkan aku. - Benarkah?</font>

2
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:16,450
<font color="yellow">Untuk apa?</font>

3
00:00:16,450 --> 00:00:18,480
<font color="yellow">Sebesar apa penyesalanmu?</font>

4
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,760
<font color="yellow">Berani sekali...</font>

5
00:00:23,650 --> 00:00:25,280
<font color="yellow">Berani sekali orang sepertimu...</font>

6
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:29,840
<font color="yellow">Kamu bahkan tidak pantas menerima rasa cemburuku!</font>

7
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:32,880
<font color="yellow">Maaf.</font>

8
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:34,640
<font color="yellow">Aku bersungguh-sungguh.</font>

9
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:39,000
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak bermaksud melukaimu.</font>

10
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:40,360
<font color="yellow">Aku sungguh-sungguh...</font>

11
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:44,800
<font color="yellow">Jika kamu menyesal, matilah.</font>

12
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:49,080
<font color="yellow">Jika kamu merasa bersalah, pergi dan bunuh dirimu.</font>

13
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:51,680
<font color="yellow">Bunuh diri agar Ji Tae</font>

14
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:53,720
<font color="yellow">tidak bisa kembali kepadamu!</font>

15
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:10,920
<font color="yellow">Joon Young.</font>

16
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,560
<font color="yellow">Aku bermimpi semalam.</font>

17
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,640
<font color="yellow">Di mimpi itu,</font>

18
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,000
<font color="yellow">aku bertemu denganmu.</font>

19
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,480
<font color="yellow">Sayangnya, aku bertemu denganmu dalam momen paling menyedihkan,</font>

20
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:41,080
<font color="yellow">paling memalukan,</font>

21
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,000
<font color="yellow">dan paling buruk dalam hidupku.</font>

22
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,400
<font color="yellow">Pintu akan tertutup.</font>

23
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:30,890
<font color="yellow">Apa mantelmu memakan semua makananmu?</font>

24
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,720
<font color="yellow">Mantel yang buruk.</font>

25
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,280
<font color="yellow">Kamu pasti lapar.</font>

26
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:44,360
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu itu hanya mimpi,</font>

27
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,760
<font color="yellow">tapi aku merasa gembira</font>

28
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,720
<font color="yellow">dan jantungku berdebar-debar.</font>

29
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:52,320
<font color="yellow">Tanganmu juga sangat hangat.</font>

30
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,520
<font color="yellow">Kamu lapar, bukan?</font>

31
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,040
<font color="yellow">Cobalah.</font>

32
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,840
<font color="yellow">Walaupun terlihat buruk, rasanya lezat.</font>

33
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,560
<font color="yellow">Aku serius.</font>

34
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,080
<font color="yellow">Ayolah.</font>

35
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,000
<font color="yellow">Jangan dimakan.</font>

36
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,600
<font color="yellow">Aku serius. Jangan dimakan.</font>

37
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:13,360
<font color="yellow">Kamu akan mati karena makan itu.</font>

38
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,720
<font color="yellow">Ini makanan pertama yang pernah kamu buat untukku.</font>

39
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:22,200
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana mungkin aku tidak memakannya?</font>

40
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,720
<font color="yellow">Meskipun aku tahu itu hanya mimpi,</font>

41
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,040
<font color="yellow">dan rasanya benar-benar tidak enak.</font>

42
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,640
<font color="yellow">Apakah kamu punya kimchi?</font>

43
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,720
<font color="yellow">Tentu aku punya kimchi.</font>

44
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,680
<font color="yellow">Kamu tidak tahu betapa sunyi,</font>

45
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,200
<font color="yellow">sepi, dan kosong rasanya</font>

46
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,800
<font color="yellow">berada dalam mimpi</font>

47
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,600
<font color="yellow">jika kamu sudah tahu itu hanya mimpi.</font>

48
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:39,180
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya aku sakit flu.</font>

49
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:40,810
<font color="yellow">Hentikanlah.</font>

50
00:05:40,810 --> 00:05:42,380
<font color="yellow">- Ini karena fluku. - Sudah kubilang, hentikanlah.</font>

51
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:43,380
<font color="yellow">Hei.</font>

52
00:05:58,780 --> 00:05:59,960
<font color="yellow">Kemari.</font>

53
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,480
<font color="yellow">Kemarilah.</font>

54
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,000
<font color="yellow">Kamu baik-baik saja?</font>

55
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,520
<font color="yellow">Pagi, jangan datang.</font>

56
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:35,180
<font color="yellow">Kumohon jangan datang.</font>

57
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:11,250
<font color="yellow">Jika ada yang berani membangunkanku dari mimpi ini,</font>

58
00:07:12,530 --> 00:07:14,930
<font color="yellow">aku akan mengikuti mereka selamanya untuk membalas dendam.</font>

59
00:08:12,850 --> 00:08:15,290
<font color="yellow">Setidaknya biarkan aku merasa bersalah kepadamu.</font>

60
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:18,710
<font color="yellow">- Kumohon. - Aku pasti akan membunuhnya.</font>

61
00:08:18,710 --> 00:08:20,810
<font color="yellow">- Jeong Eun. - Aku akan membunuhnya</font>

62
00:08:21,850 --> 00:08:23,010
<font color="yellow">dengan kedua tanganku.</font>

63
00:08:23,490 --> 00:08:24,900
<font color="yellow">Kamu pikir aku tidak bisa?</font>

64
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:27,850
<font color="yellow">Akan kulakukan apa pun demi mendapatkanmu kembali, Ji Tae.</font>

65
00:08:30,370 --> 00:08:31,690
<font color="yellow">Bukankah sekali saja sudah cukup?</font>

66
00:08:33,970 --> 00:08:35,450
<font color="yellow">- Apa? - Karena sikapmu yang tidak dewasa</font>

67
00:08:35,450 --> 00:08:37,450
<font color="yellow">dan egois, kamu pernah membahayakan nyawa seseorang.</font>

68
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:40,690
<font color="yellow">Bukankah itu sudah cukup?</font>

69
00:08:43,810 --> 00:08:45,170
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu?</font>

70
00:08:45,170 --> 00:08:46,610
<font color="yellow">Maksudku kamu tidak boleh</font>

71
00:08:48,170 --> 00:08:50,740
<font color="yellow">semudah itu mengatakan akan membunuh seseorang.</font>

72
00:08:53,610 --> 00:08:54,610
<font color="yellow">Kamu tidak boleh pergi.</font>

73
00:08:55,450 --> 00:08:57,120
<font color="yellow">- Jeong Eun. - Jangan pergi menemuinya.</font>

74
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,740
<font color="yellow">- Lepaskan aku. - Ini hari ulang tahunku, Ji Tae.</font>

75
00:09:01,370 --> 00:09:02,490
<font color="yellow">Tinggallah bersamaku.</font>

76
00:09:02,490 --> 00:09:03,570
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan aku!</font>

77
00:09:04,050 --> 00:09:05,930
<font color="yellow">- Aku tidak bisa. - Lepaskan dia.</font>

78
00:09:20,610 --> 00:09:22,410
<font color="yellow">Biarkan dia pergi. Kamu bisa menghabiskan waktu denganku.</font>

79
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:25,980
<font color="yellow">Suruh dia pergi</font>

80
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:28,450
<font color="yellow">dan rayakan ulang tahunmu bersamaku.</font>

81
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:50,250
<font color="yellow">Eul.</font>

82
00:10:22,930 --> 00:10:25,530
<font color="yellow">"Ji Tae"</font>

83
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:34,560
<font color="yellow">Ini</font>

84
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,360
<font color="yellow">sebagai pengganti sepatumu yang rusak.</font>

85
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,480
<font color="yellow">Ini adalah hadiah ulang tahunmu.</font>

86
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,480
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih sudah selalu</font>

87
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,800
<font color="yellow">- menyelamatkan aku. - Aku tahu.</font>

88
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:49,000
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah seperti malaikat penyelamatmu.</font>

89
00:10:51,290 --> 00:10:53,140
<font color="yellow">Kamu tidak mau menerima hadiah ulang tahunmu?</font>

90
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:54,410
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kamu melakukan ini kepadaku?</font>

91
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,730
<font color="yellow">Kupikir kamu tidak mau menggodaku.</font>

92
00:10:57,730 --> 00:10:59,040
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kamu membuat hatiku goyah?</font>

93
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,720
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana kamu tahu ini hari ulang tahunku?</font>

94
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,040
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana jika aku mencoba membuat hatimu goyah?</font>

95
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,360
<font color="yellow">Apakah itu bisa berhasil?</font>

96
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:15,340
<font color="yellow">Bukan karena kamu ingin membalas dendam kepada Eul</font>

97
00:11:15,340 --> 00:11:17,610
<font color="yellow">karena telah merebut pria yang kamu cintai.</font>

98
00:11:17,610 --> 00:11:20,960
<font color="yellow">Bukan juga karena kamu ingin menunjukkan kepada Ji Tae</font>

99
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:24,120
<font color="yellow">apa yang dia lepaskan.</font>

100
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,160
<font color="yellow">Ini sungguh-sungguh, tanpa syarat lain,</font>

101
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,520
<font color="yellow">apakah kamu tertarik digoda olehku?</font>

102
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,480
<font color="yellow">Tidak, tunggu.</font>

103
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:36,680
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana jika kamu menggodaku?</font>

104
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,260
<font color="yellow">Tapi kamu menyukai Eul.</font>

105
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:41,520
<font color="yellow">Karena itu aku memintamu untuk menggodaku.</font>

106
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,760
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin melupakan semua hal</font>

107
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,600
<font color="yellow">tentang Eul.</font>

108
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:49,440
<font color="yellow">Aku ingin memenuhi kepalaku</font>

109
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,480
<font color="yellow">dengan bayangan dirimu.</font>

110
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,920
<font color="yellow">Bisakah kamu melakukan itu?</font>

111
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:33,960
<font color="yellow">"Choi Ji Tae"</font>

112
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:39,060
<font color="yellow">Halo?</font>

113
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,270
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kamu lakukan?</font>

114
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,170
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kamu mendekati Jeong Eun?</font>

115
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:43,790
<font color="yellow">Untuk membantumu, Ji Tae.</font>

116
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:48,710
<font color="yellow">Aku akan membantumu menyingkirkan wanita itu.</font>

117
00:12:49,190 --> 00:12:50,310
<font color="yellow">Bukankah seharusnya kamu berterima kasih?</font>

118
00:12:50,950 --> 00:12:52,150
<font color="yellow">Kamu berterima kasih, bukan?</font>

119
00:12:52,470 --> 00:12:55,150
<font color="yellow">Tidak masalah. Kita harus saling membantu seperti ini.</font>

120
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:58,030
<font color="yellow">Aku harus melakukan sesuatu yang baik sebelum aku mati.</font>

121
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:59,290
<font color="yellow">Hei, Joon Young!</font>

122
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:02,230
<font color="yellow">Jika kamu berterima kasih, traktir aku minum nanti.</font>

123
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:25,930
<font color="yellow">Hei, apa yang akan kamu lakukan?</font>

124
00:13:25,930 --> 00:13:28,150
<font color="yellow">Mereka mengambil semuanya.</font>

125
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:30,790
<font color="yellow">Dasar...</font>

126
00:13:35,070 --> 00:13:36,070
<font color="yellow">Itu barang-barang yang kamu buang.</font>

127
00:13:36,070 --> 00:13:38,670
<font color="yellow">Orang-orang mengambil semuanya dari baju, tas, sampai sepatu.</font>

128
00:13:39,430 --> 00:13:41,210
<font color="yellow">Mereka hanya meninggalkan bungkusan kosong ini.</font>

129
00:13:41,210 --> 00:13:45,080
<font color="yellow">Sekarang kita tidak bisa menjual atau mengembalikannya.</font>

130
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,230
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan kamu lakukan?</font>

131
00:13:47,870 --> 00:13:48,990
<font color="yellow">Kamu ingin aku membelinya lagi?</font>

132
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:52,290
<font color="yellow">- Omonganmu konyol. - Aduh!</font>

133
00:13:52,290 --> 00:13:54,110
<font color="yellow">Sadarkah kamu apa yang telah kamu lakukan?</font>

134
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:57,310
<font color="yellow">Kita tidak membahas tentang satu atau sepuluh dolar.</font>

135
00:13:57,310 --> 00:13:59,430
<font color="yellow">Kamu menghabiskan 10.000 dolar dalam semalam.</font>

136
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:03,410
<font color="yellow">Aku bilang akan membelikannya lagi untukmu. Aku kaya.</font>

137
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:04,550
<font color="yellow">Dasar...</font>

138
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:06,790
<font color="yellow">Aku akan memberi tahu Jik.</font>

139
00:14:07,990 --> 00:14:10,750
<font color="yellow">Aku akan memberitahunya bahwa kamu menerima</font>

140
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:11,910
<font color="yellow">satu juta dolar agar kamu bisa</font>

141
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:13,750
<font color="yellow">membiayai kuliahnya dan mengirimnya ke luar negeri.</font>

142
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:17,450
<font color="yellow">Kamu ingin memutuskan hubunganku dengannya?</font>

143
00:14:17,450 --> 00:14:19,850
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu, cepat kembalikan uangnya sebelum dia tahu.</font>

144
00:14:19,850 --> 00:14:22,290
<font color="yellow">Tidak masalah jika kamu berutang, tapi pastikan</font>

145
00:14:22,290 --> 00:14:24,350
<font color="yellow">kamu mengembalikan semua uang yang kamu terima dari mereka.</font>

146
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:28,830
<font color="yellow">Siapa?</font>

147
00:14:34,990 --> 00:14:36,270
<font color="yellow">Hyun Woo. Bukan.</font>

148
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:37,750
<font color="yellow">Ji Tae.</font>

149
00:14:38,310 --> 00:14:40,270
<font color="yellow">Suruh dia pergi. Aku tidak mau menemuinya.</font>

150
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:43,750
<font color="yellow">Eul menyuruhmu pergi</font>

151
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:47,750
<font color="yellow">dan dia tidak ingin bertemu denganmu lagi.</font>

152
00:15:19,310 --> 00:15:20,790
<font color="yellow">Astaga, apa ini?</font>

153
00:15:26,710 --> 00:15:29,270
<font color="yellow">Hei, kamu tidak perlu melakukan ini.</font>

154
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:31,600
<font color="yellow">Cobalah.</font>

155
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,830
<font color="yellow">Haruskah?</font>

156
00:15:42,710 --> 00:15:43,710
<font color="yellow">Apa aku terlihat cantik?</font>

157
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:45,610
<font color="yellow">Tentu saja.</font>

158
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:46,630
<font color="yellow">Hentikan itu.</font>

159
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:50,180
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kalian berdua lakukan?</font>

160
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:51,990
<font color="yellow">- Begini... - Berhenti.</font>

161
00:15:52,310 --> 00:15:53,310
<font color="yellow">Hei.</font>

162
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:58,510
<font color="yellow">Kudengar tempat ini dikelola oleh ibu Shin Joon Young.</font>

163
00:15:58,910 --> 00:16:01,490
<font color="yellow">Tahukah kamu bahwa dia suka menggoda wanita?</font>

164
00:16:01,490 --> 00:16:02,790
<font color="yellow">Ya, aku sudah dengar itu.</font>

165
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:06,030
<font color="yellow">Kudengar dia tidak bisa tidur tanpa wanita di sampingnya.</font>

166
00:16:06,550 --> 00:16:07,950
<font color="yellow">Aku dengar dia berganti pacar</font>

167
00:16:08,310 --> 00:16:10,080
<font color="yellow">setiap sepuluh jam. Tidak, setiap tiga jam.</font>

168
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:12,750
<font color="yellow">Kenapa wanita menyukainya?</font>

169
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:15,280
<font color="yellow">Berhenti memikirkan itu, Gook Young.</font>

170
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:17,230
<font color="yellow">Kamu bukan manajer Joon Young lagi.</font>

171
00:16:17,550 --> 00:16:19,240
<font color="yellow">Kamu manajer restoran ini.</font>

172
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,270
<font color="yellow">Berhentilah memikirkan itu.</font>

173
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:22,550
<font color="yellow">Hei, kudengar Shin Joon Young</font>

174
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:24,870
<font color="yellow">menjadi lebih tinggi karena operasi plastik.</font>

175
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:27,210
<font color="yellow">Kakakku melihatnya di rumah sakit.</font>

176
00:16:27,210 --> 00:16:28,790
<font color="yellow">Astaga, benarkah?</font>

177
00:16:29,590 --> 00:16:32,890
<font color="yellow">Aku ibunya, dan aku tidak tahu itu.</font>

178
00:16:32,890 --> 00:16:36,050
<font color="yellow">Apakah dia menjalani
operasi plastik</font>

179
00:16:36,050 --> 00:16:38,210
<font color="yellow">untuk seluruh wajah
dan tingginya?</font>

180
00:16:38,210 --> 00:16:39,410
<font color="yellow">Begini,</font>

181
00:16:39,410 --> 00:16:41,790
<font color="yellow">aku akan memberi kalian uang</font>

182
00:16:41,790 --> 00:16:43,670
<font color="yellow">agar kalian juga bisa menjalani operasi plastik.</font>

183
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:46,230
<font color="yellow">Kalian bisa mengubah wajah jelek kalian</font>

184
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:49,030
<font color="yellow">dengan wajah yang tampan seperti Joon Young.</font>

185
00:16:49,590 --> 00:16:51,250
<font color="yellow">Kalian juga bisa berhenti hidup sebagai orang kerdil</font>

186
00:16:51,250 --> 00:16:55,200
<font color="yellow">dan menjadi tinggi lewat operasi seperti Joon Young.</font>

187
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,650
<font color="yellow">Dasar orang bodoh.</font>

188
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:58,670
<font color="yellow">Kenapa Ibu berbicara seperti itu kepada pelanggan?</font>

189
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:00,990
<font color="yellow">Astaga. Cepat foto. Itu Shin Joon Young.</font>

